QuestData.Title: Adventurers Wanted: Gnomeregan
QuestData.Description: King Anduin Wrynn has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Gnomeregan,west of Ironforge, immediately!$B$BThe Gnomes need help reclaiming their city! If you so choose, head to Gnomeregan and speak with Murd Doc, recruiter for the G-Team, to help in the mission.
